content: Identify with who you want to be instead of being dragged down by who you think you are
I felt very little intrinsic value, and my self worth is attached to people and environment
Everyone is kinda fucked up on the inside even if they do not show it
I spend so much time pondering what to read, how to read it, how to record down what I learned, that I never can commit to reading
We often confine ourselves to images of what we think other people think of us
